{"type":"message","id":"f5ecee81","parentId":"a8b9de66","timestamp":"2026-04-30T15:18:18.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The regular memory files (non-dreaming) don't seem to have Amy/Royal Cove info. Let me check the dreaming/light files more specifically for time-related info. The dreaming/light files seem to be where the email summaries are stored. Let me try a different approach - check if there's any timestamp data in the email reports themselves.\n\nActually, I should check if I can access Bobby's email to look at actual timestamps from Amy. But I don't have direct Gmail access right now. Let me think about what I know:\n\nFrom the memory context, I know:\n- Amy Smith is the leasing agent at Royal Cove (RC Leasing)\n- She replied on April 13 to Bobby's inquiry\n- She's been sending emails about the rental application\n- She uses RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com\n\n\n- The emails I've seen have timestamps in the morning hours (between 11:34 AM and 1:05 PM), so I should look for more specific timing patterns in the email logs.\n","thinkingSignature":"a5136b21d04f04dc6416f61138d7f0a95e2ae7c97134f03cc54214fa8edf80ca"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q1tkk57uf73k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -h \"📬\\|ICLOUD\\|GMAIL\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/memory/dreaming/light/2026-04-*.md | grep -i \"Amy\\|Royal Cove\\|RC Leasing\" | grep -oP \"\\d{1,2}:\\d{2} [AP]M\" | sort | uniq -c | sort -k2"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":310,"cacheRead":32960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33427,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777562282067,"responseId":"0642a5aa90f7d2641fd11c5ac92e5ea9"}}
