🟡 IMPORTANT: • RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment (Apr 13) └ Royal Cove apartments in Poughkeepsie — 1BR from $1825, 2BR from $2150, includes heat/hot water ⚪ LOW PRIORITY: • Taylor Alexander — Re: Apartment Inquiry (Ja\n- Candidate: Assistant: 📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (2 in inbox) 🟡 IMPORTANT: • RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment └ Reply from Royal Cove apartments in Poughkeepsie — 1BR from $1,825/mo, pool, pet-friendly. Leasing agent Amy Smith followed up on your April inquiry. • Taylor Alexander — Re:\n- Candidate: Assistant: 📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (2 new) 🟡 IMPORTANT: • RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment └ Royal Cove apartments in Poughkeepsie, 1BR from $1825/mo, heat included ⚪ LOW PRIORITY: • Taylor Alexander — Re: Apartment Inquiry (Around mid June) └ 2BR from $2265/mo including\n- Candidate: Assistant: Done — Gmail check complete (1 important email about your Royal Cove rental application, needing document verification), and iCloud check done (no new emails). 🦋📧\n- Candidate: Assistant: 📬 **GMAIL** — 1 new email (iHeart newsletter, low priority) 📬 **ICLOUD** — 2 inbox messages (apartment-related replies from RC Leasing and Taylor Alexander from your recent apartment search — not new today, just unread in iCloud)\n- Candidate: Assistant: 📬 GMAIL — No new emails 📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (2 total, oldest from Apr 13 — likely pre-existing) • RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment (Apr 13) • Taylor Alexander — Re: Apartment Inquiry (Jan 22) These iCloud emails aren't new — they're just showing because the\n- Candidate: Assistant: I found the Royal Cove email (the one sent today about your rental application), but I don't see any email **from Amy** in your inbox. The Royal Cove emails are from `no-reply@docuverus.com` and `royalcove@lexingtonpg.com` — no Amy there. Do you mean: 1. **A different\n- Candidate: Assistant: Found it! Amy Smith from RC Leasing (Royal Cove) replied to your inquiry on April 13. Here's the context: She confirmed pricing: **1BR starting at $1,825/mo**, pet fee $400 (dogs), and the income requirement is 2.5x monthly rent with a 600+ credit score. Want me to dra\n- Candidate: Assistant: Done! ✉️ Email sent to Amy at RC Leasing. Here's what went out: > **To:** RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com > **Subject:** Re: Looking for new apartment > > Hi Amy, > > I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental applicati\n- Candidate: Assistant: Oh no, I already sent it! 🚨 Unfortunately the email went out via SMTP — it's unrecoverable now. What do you want to do? I can: 1. **Send a follow-up** to clarify or correct anything 2. **Wait for Amy's reply** and respond when she writes back Sorry about that — I shou\n- Candidate: Assistant: Got it! Here's the draft: --- **To:** RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com **Subject:** Re: Looking for new apartment --- Hi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting\n- Candidate: Assistant: Done — both email checks sent to Telegram. Gmail had 2 new promotional emails (Clipp discount + Netflix win-back offer), and iCloud has 2 older apartment inquiry threads from RC Leasing and Taylor Alexander.\n- Candidate: Assistant: Both reports sent to Bobby ✓ **GMAIL:** 1 new email — Royal Cove rental application needs document uploads (income, ID verification). ⚠️ Action needed. **ICLOUD:** No new emails.\n- Candidate: Assistant: 📬 GMAIL — New Mail (1 new) 🟡 IMPORTANT: • Royal Cove — Your Rental Application with Royal Cove └ 🚨 Action needed: Upload income, ID & documentation to verify your rental application. Click the link in the email to complete the process.\n- Candidate: Assistant: 📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (2 unread in inbox) 🟡 IMPORTANT: • RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment (Apr 13) └ Royal Cove apartments in Poughkeepsie — 1BR from $1825, 2BR from $2150, includes heat/hot water ⚪ LOW PRIORITY: • Taylor Alexander — Re: Apartment 